  "version_pin_rationale": "libxcb-extras umbrella catalog covering 13 libxcb-* family .debs (dri2, dri3, composite, icccm4, present, randr, render, render-util, res, shm, sync, xfixes, xinput) that wlroots + Mesa + sway probe at runtime. THIS WAS THE HIDDEN DE0-G DEP CALLED OUT BY THE DE0-G REPORT. Bundled as ONE catalog (rather than 13 separate ones) to keep the catalog-file count manageable; the dependency_closure[] lists libxcb1 as the single parent. Two .debs in this set ship from non-libxcb1 source packages: libxcb-icccm4 (xcb-util-wm 0.4.1-1.1build2) and libxcb-render-util0 (xcb-util-renderutil 0.3.9-1build3); their version pins are encoded in the version string suffix and in the per-deb deb_url + deb_sha256. The mixed-version umbrella is a deliberate convenience; if a future regression needs to bisect ONE libxcb-* version independently, split it into its own catalog. Note that DE-H1's catalog count goes up by 1 here instead of 13."
}
